
PROPERTIES NEEDED IN THE STRUCT:

Borders:
    Yes/No/Transparent
    List
        Coordinated corners?

Positions:
    Width
    Internal border
    Start X pos
    Start Y pos

Text Modes:
    Instant or delayed
        (If 0, is instant, otherwise decode to sec/millisec)
    Stat mode [ LOREM IPSUM:     234 ]
        Yes/No
        Description Text
        Numeric
    Quote mode? [Text, blank line, right-aligned name]

Content:
    Text
    Numbers
    Quotee [ extra line, end of it, name]

Highlights:
    Bold or not


